<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="turn-away">turn away</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>把…转过去；把…打发走：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She turned her head away, feeling too ashamed to meet his gaze. 
因为害羞而不敢和他对视，她把头转了过去。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Because the hall was full, many people were turned away. 
因礼堂满了，许多人被打发走了。</p></div></div>